# List of State Register of Heritage Places in the Shire of Narembeen

The State Register of Heritage Places is maintained by the Heritage Council of Western Australia. , 172 places are heritage-listed in the Shire of Narembeen, of which five are on the State Register of Heritage Places.
List
The Western Australian State Register of Heritage Places, , lists the following five state registered places within the Shire of Narembeen:
